OL,6,FA mother and her two children who were
OL,7,Fkilled during a blaze at their home on
OL,8,FBoxing Day died from "exposure to the
OL,9,Fcombustion products of fire", an
OL,10,Finquest has heard.
OL,12,FFionnghuala Shearman, known as Nu, 38,
OL,13,Fseven-year-old Eve and Ohner, who was
OL,14,Ffour, were killed when fire swept
OL,15,Fthrough their terraced cottage home in
OL,16,FBrimscombe Hill in the early hours of
OL,17,F26 December.
OL,19,FPolice officer Tom Shearman attempted
OL,20,Fto rescue his family but was forced
OL,21,Fback by the severity of the flames.
