OL,6,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,7,Fmid-terrace cottage on Brimscombe Hill
OL,8,Fat about 3am.
OL,10,FKaty Skerrett, senior coroner for
OL,11,FGloucestershire, opened three separate
OL,12,Finquests into the deaths of Mrs
OL,13,FShearman and her two children at
OL,14,FGloucestershire coroner's court on
OL,15,FMonday.
OL,17,FOutlining the circumstances of the
OL,18,Fdeaths, Ms Skerrett told the court:
OL,19,F"The fire service was contacted at
OL,20,F3.12am on December 26th by a neighbour
OL,21,Freporting that there was a fire.
