OL,9,Fthat blaze.
OL,11,F"It was established that only one of
OL,12,Fthe four occupants had managed to
OL,13,Fescape the cottage alive, Tom Shearman.
OL,15,F"The other three occupants were unable
OL,16,Fto exit the house due to the fire and
OL,17,Fsmoke which engulfed the property.
