OL,6,FNo members of the Shearman family
OL,7,Fattended the brief hearing, which
OL,8,Flasted less than 10 minutes.
OL,10,FPolice believe the fire started on the
OL,11,Fground floor and investigations are
OL,12,Fongoing to establish the cause, but it
OL,13,Fis not being treated as suspicious.
OL,15,FThe fire destroyed the roof, the
OL,16,Fceilings and the stairs, as well as
OL,17,Fcausing other significant internal
OL,18,Fdamage.
OL,20,FA fundraising campaign for the family
OL,21,Fhas so far raised nearly #440,000.
